    <stitle>FRONT NON-DRIVE STEERING AXLE: ROCKWELL - LUBRICATION AND MAINTENANCE - OIL-LUBRICATED WHEEL BEARINGS
    </stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="assemble" graphiccount="1">
        <title>OIL-LUBRICATED WHEEL BEARINGS</title>
        <para>Check the level on the cap. If the oil level is not at the specified level on the cap, remove the fill
            plug. Add oil until the oil is at the specified level (
            <hotlnk xrefid="f0200546">Figure 46</hotlnk>). Refer to GROUP 10 - LUBRICATION in the CTS-5000 Master
            Service Manual for recommended lubes.
        </para>
        <figure id="f0200546" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g0200546" filename="../figg02/G0200546.webp" type="webp"/>
            <caption>Figure 46. Oil at Specified Level</caption>
